closely, except for SVD component 2 which matches AO
more closely. However, since AO is defined as the first prin-
cipal component of the region located to the north of 20N,
it is not surprising to find that one of the SVD components
of our world-wide SLP data --the second component--is
highly correlated with the AO index.
